# Frontend Environment Variables
# ==================================

# API Base URL - Uncomment and set for production deployment
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://your-server-ip:7777

# Development configuration
# The app will auto-detect the server URL based on current hostname
# - localhost/127.0.0.1: uses http://localhost:7777
# - Remote access: uses http://[current-ip]:7777

# Production example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.100:7777